snippet.title: ★ Rockman Dash [Megaman Legends]  Trailer - Playstation Magazine  [05-12-1997] ★
snippet.description:
This comes in Official PlayStation Magazine Demo Disc - Volume 6
Released Date Disc : March 1998
the record is dated in 05/12/1997

There are two sections on an OPM Demo Disc: Videos and Playable Demos. For Disc 6, they are:

Watch video:

Alundra
Saga Frontier
Rockman Dash
NBA Shootout '98

Playable games:

Bloody Roar
Shipwreckers
Monster Rancher
